snippet.title: Captain Wayne Vacation Desperation | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Thar be a storm brewin' and his NAME IS CAPTAIN WAYNE

Captain Wayne is an intense, fast-action Retro Shooter about a sailor with a SHOTGUN for an ARM!! With a cartoony, hand-drawn art style and brutal gameplay, you'll have to mow down enemies through 8 action-packed locales to take back what's yours. ARE YOU READY TO RAISE ANCHOR?
